What I learnt
Maltego is a very powerful tool used in OSINT investigation for visualizing relationships for a specific target. It is needed to run various transforms to get a bigger picture and more available information. As noted in the first practice using theHarvester, having no result or little result is still useful information because it means that the target has little footprint.
